      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 1903: `cloneConversationFrom(convId, uri)` is scheduled once per remote member. If a conversation has multiple remote members, this can launch concurrent recovery clones for the same corrupted repository, racing over the same on-disk path/backups and potentially replacing a successful clone with another in-flight attempt. Schedule one recovery operation per conversation, or serialize attempts so the next member is tried only after the previous source fails.\n```suggestion\n                    scheduled \u003d true;\n                    shared-\u003ecloneConversationFrom(convId, uriIt-\u003esecond);\n                    break;\n```",
